WEBVTT

00:12:24.014 --> 00:12:30.196
He looks very inward, he waits and waits
until things are right,

00:12:30.220 --> 00:12:31.687
and he broods,

00:12:31.711 --> 00:12:33.909
and you end up feeling,

00:12:33.933 --> 00:12:36.339
"What's the matter here,
does he not like me?"

00:12:36.363 --> 00:12:38.847
You know, he can make you quite insecure.

00:12:38.871 --> 00:12:41.910
AdG: So John looked for ways
to make a personal connection.

00:12:41.934 --> 00:12:44.767
You can almost imagine him
on an 11-hour phone call.

00:12:45.196 --> 00:12:48.976
JL: There came a moment
when I revealed to Stephen

00:12:49.000 --> 00:12:53.055
that I had become a huge fan
of English Premier League soccer.

00:12:53.682 --> 00:12:56.794
And at that point
he opened up like a flower.

00:12:57.259 --> 00:12:58.726
By the end of that ...

00:12:59.707 --> 00:13:03.903
You know, suddenly there was this
animated conversation between us,